quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  28,61,Mbega wamuntu twemerera indagano nziza kandi akazoyironka mbega azongana nuwo twahezagiye kumahirwe yo ng’aha kw’Isi gusa hanyuma k’umusi w’imperuka abe mubantu bazoshengezwa mu muriro udahera
  28,62,"N’umusi Imana izoba hamagara hanyuma ivuge iti:- bari hehe basomambike banje mwamye mwihayisha yuko turi kumwe nabo"
  28,63,"Bazovuga bamwe bashikiwe kuribo niyo mvugo bati:- Muremyi wacu aba bantu nibo twazimije, tubazimiza nkuko natwe twazimiye rero turabikuyeko imbere yawe kandi ntibasenga twebwe"
  28,64,"Hazovurwa hati:- nimuba hamagare basomambike banyu, mubisanzwe bazo hamagarwa mugabo ntibazobitaba ariko bazobona ibihano iyo bobaye mu bantu barongotse"
  28,65,"N’umusi Imana izoba hamagara hanyuma ize ivuge iti:- mbega mwishuye iki zantumwa z’Imana"
  28,66,"Inkuru z’uwo musi bazozibagira, nabo ntibazo shobora kubazanya icarico cose"
  28,67,"Nayo uwasavye ikigongwe nukwemera hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nkumbure yoba ari mubazoba bafise intsinzi"
  28,68,"N’umuremyi wawe arema uko yishakiye akitorera uko yishakiye, abantu ntibanegura kuko iri kure nigabanukirwa ry’ibintu ivyarivyo vyose, kandi irisukuye nabo bayi gereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  28,69,N’umuremyi wawe arafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo ibikiriza vyabo binyegeza hamwe n’ivyo baserura
  28,70,"Nayo niyo Mana atayindi isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene rudende, ihayagizwa ryose ryiza haba muntango canke kw’iherezo ryayo ryose nirwiwe, n’amategeko yayo yose n’amwe, mwese muzosubizwa iwe"
  28,71,"Vuga uti:- nimumbwire yuko Imana igize ir’ijoro ngo rigume ari ijoro gusa kugeza k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi n’iyihe Mana atari Imana izoba garurira uwo muco? mbega mwebwe ntimwumva"
  28,72,"Vuga uti:- ni mumbwire yuko Imana igize umutaga ngo ugume ari umutaga gusa kugeza k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi n’iyihe Mana atari Imana yonyene izoba garurira iryo joro? mbega mwebwe ntimubona"
  28,73,"Kubera impuhwe zayo, yarabagiriye Ijoro n’Umutaga kugira ngo muruhukire muri iryo joro nukurironderera mwo imigisha yaryo kugira ngo mushime"
  28,74,"N’umusi izoba hamagara nukuvumera iti:- bari hehe basomambike banje mwamye mwihayisha yuko turi kumwe nabo"
  28,75,"Tuzokura mu bantu babe ivyabona hanyuma tuze tubabwire duti:- nimuzane ibirego vyanyu, aho niho bazoca bamenya yuko ukuri kuri ku Mana kandi bazotakaza ivyo bahora badukana navyo"